POLAR CAN HELP  


We have over 30 years of experience and we are a leading US manufacturer of cooling vests and hot/cold therapy products. Join our team: become a distributor! We are proud suppliers for the MS Cooling Programs offered by the Multiple Sclerosis Association of America and the Multiple Sclerosis Foundation. Polar has a GSA Contract to supply our
products to the US Military and VA Hospitals nationwide. Medical professionals and non-profit organizations use our customized products as a marketing tool. Let us know how we can partner with you too!  


