Event Details
TowerXchange Meetups are unique executive retreats for the most influential men and women in telecoms infrastructure. Our longest running event, the TowerXchange Meetup Africa and Middle East enters its 5th year in 2017, returning to Johannesburg on 3-4 October.
80-90% of the leading towercos and MNOs attend
At other telecom events, a maximum of around 10-15% of the CXOs who lead tower strategy for MNOs and towercos are in attendance. At TowerXchange we regularly attract multiple senior representatives from 80-90% of the towercos active in any region, as well as the majority of MNOs. And thanks to our unique structured networking roundtables, everyone has access to these decision makers.










Timeoctober 3 (Tuesday) - 4 (Wednesday) UTC+02:00






